    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: 12th level, Pact of the Chain feature</em><br />You can bind a creature that you can see within 60 feet in magical chains of force as an action. When you do so, the target must make a Strength saving throw against your spell DC. If they fail, they are restrained.</p><p>If they fail the initial Strength saving throw then they are paralyzed until the end of your next turn. On their turn they, if they are not paralyzed, may use their action to attempt to free themselves from the chains by making a Strength saving throw. The chains disappear when the creature breaks free, after one minute has passed, or when you use Chains of Carceri again.</p><p>This may be invoked in place of one of your Eldritch Blast beams.</p>",
